@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_grsjio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 + wp.sin((tmp + 0.90 * v2 + 0.98)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin((v0 + 0.69 + v2 + 0.40)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = 0.75
    data[tid] = v0
